title: The Doors Concerto (Riders on the Storm)
description:
The Doors Concerto (Riders on the Storm)

Jaz Coleman (arranger)
Nigel Kennedy (violin)
Peter Scholes (conductor)
Colin Downs (classical guitar)
Chris Goody (percussion)
Rodney Clarke, Robert Anderson, Adam Greene, Alex Ashworth (chant vocals)
Praque Symphony Orchestra

Recorded at Dvorak Hall, Rudofinum, Prague; Abbey Road, Swarm West, London, England; Studio Recall, Paris, France from October to December 1999.

1. Riders On The Storm
2. The Unknown Soldier
3. Spanish Caravan
4. Love Street
5. Hello, I Love You
6. Light My Fire
7. People Are Strange
8. Strange Days
9. The End
